  }, "The passenger side galley would be built overlapping the sliding door opening but had to leave room for a \"reasonable\" opening. We didn't have a hard number for how much, but knew we needed at LEAST 24\" to comfortably enter and exit through the slider."))), mdx("p", null, "To achieve \"2\", \"3\", and \"4\", we knew we needed to keep the length and depth of both sides of the galley to be as short and shallow as possible while accommodating the appliances and structure."), mdx("p", null, "Adding constraints/requirements:"), mdx("ol", {
